  Keep all claims conservative and consultation-led (server-side comment;
  not sent to the client).
%>
<section class="consult-promise">
    <h2 class="section-title">How our consultation works</h2>
    <p class="section-sub">A calm, consultation-first approach — private by design, with no public candidate database.</p>
    <div class="how-trust-grid consult-steps">
        <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-step-num">1</span>
            <h3>We understand your family&rsquo;s needs</h3>
            <p>We start with a conversation about your household, your routine, and the qualities that matter most to you.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-step-num">2</span>
            <h3>We suggest suitable candidates privately</h3>
            <p>You receive a small, considered shortlist matched to your home &mdash; shared privately, never from a public list.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="how-step">
            <span class="how-step-num">3</span>
