            <p>Full CVs and reference details are shared only after consultation, when an introduction is genuinely moving forward.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
    <ul class="reassurance-row" aria-label="How we protect privacy">
        <li><span class="reassure-icon">&#128274;</span> No public candidate database</li>
        <li><span class="reassure-icon">&#128737;</span> Candidate privacy protected</li>
        <li><span class="reassure-icon">&#9989;</span> References available by request</li>
    </ul>
</section>
